short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Be informed when SunfyreTV is streaming.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The SunfyreTV extension notifies you when SunfyreTV starts a new stream. If you miss the notification don't worry, there will be a "Live" badge on the extension icon to make sure you don't miss the stream.
You will also find links to her Twitter, Instagram, Discord YouTube and Twitch.
